column1: # The estimated aggregate reading for January-May 1868 has been omitted.
# The reading of 6.92 for November-December 1869 is an aggregate for the two months.
# The reading of 3.73 for January-February 1871 is an aggregate for the two months.
# The reading of 4.92 for January-February 1873 is an aggregate for the two months.
# The observer, Mr G.W.Wray, lived at Grove House, Leyburn.
